@Togetherdec @TheFreds @ChildrensUnion @sajidjavid @MHRAgovuk @CMO_England @10DowningStreet @UKHSA Weren’t you the ones complaining about having choice over vaccines? 

Defending your right to choose?

Now you’re fighting to take that choice away from others?

Kinda tarnishes all your work on equality, liberal attitudes and freedom of choice.
